{"tid":2121382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【走定唔走】歸納出香港而家多種人","createTime":"2020-07-23T09:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T10:18:50.000Z","uid":61443,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c084c085a8f7c6dc1baeff22c771d444ce76f576","tid":2121382,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"1. <br />\n平時吃喝換樂，<br />\n而家都係吃喝玩樂。<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n香港只會愈嚟愈好，<br />\n因為有同志們支持。<br />\n<br />\n3. <br />\n知道未來愈嚟愈差，<br />\n但係走咗揾唔返而家人工。<br />\n<br />\n4.  <br />\n知道未來愈嚟愈差，<br />\n自己都係揾一萬幾千，<br />\n但係擔心過到去融入唔到。<br />\n<br />\n5. <br />\n知道未來愈嚟愈差，<br />\n自己已經冇嘢可以輸，<br />\n把握機會一定走。 <br />\n<br />\n6.<br />\n已經到咗生死存亡問題，<br />\n走就一定走硬，<br />\n盡最大努力拎到幾多有幾多就走。<br />\n<br />\n7.<br />\n已經到咗生死存亡問題，<br />\n但係生於斯長於斯，<br />\n香港是我家，留守。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你係邊種? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f5f6d095d68dfe3833c3242fbbf51b73dfe2d6","tid":2121382,"uid":4519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f0d0f601bc36e492b22897e67bbf7a8445a4c4","tid":2121382,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"歡迎補充 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac00f56501f1503ba828680a11fa3c985c40dae","tid":2121382,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9a35d6d48c1152cc13a4bb2d65ca4973ac862898","tid":2121382,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c489cee0f28fa20e1f27ad579ed5f406f8f159d1","tid":2121382,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"4+7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fbc36fbbd4b76f72a4f5fb85a22a3c02b6747c",